{
  "stem": "26983.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the headquarter in Prague and in Vienna was run by Eichmann, for Jewish immigration.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Auswanderungsamt or something like that they call it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And many Jews worked with Eichmann.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I helped them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I even remember my cousin-- who is now in America, and one  in Israel-- they worked with Eichmann in this office.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when they phoned us from Prague, and they phoned us here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Is the Gestapo Center for Jewish Emigration.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But he tried to help us also to go out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it was only in '39, '40.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He himself-- Eichmann let him go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At that time, the policy of the German was to throw out--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As many as possible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Forcefully, as many as possible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later on, it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was too small--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My family even thought maybe to immigrate to Santo Domingo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because at that time, in Santo Domingo you could get some visa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father bought a tropical hat I remember, and--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a white suit because we thought--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's good for that climate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But unfortunately, it didn't came to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was too late.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For one reason or another, there were more and more restrictions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't say.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my uncle got a certificate, as he was one of the Mizrachi leaders--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're wonderful, the Mizrachi leaders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he could go with his family to Israel and emigrated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '39, it was still possible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But his children-- one of his children are alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We heard these rumors, and then we could still read newspaper.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we read in the newspaper, in the German newspaper, that Hitler will give to the Jews a town or something in a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
